  <brief_title>Brentuximab Vedotin Associated With Chemotherapy in Untreated Patients With Hodgkin Lymphoma.</brief_title>
  <acronym>BREACH</acronym>
  <official_title>Brentuximab Vedotin Associated With Chemotherapy in Untreated Patients With Stage I/II Unfavourable Hodgkin Lymphoma. A Randomized Phase II LYSA-FIL-EORTC Intergroup Study</official_title>
